On OS MOBILE is a lightweight high-hardware integrated device that integrates payment methods such as bank cards WeChat Alipay ApplePayand membership cards. It also integrates printing hardware and 4G modules to solve mobile scenarios without space constraints. With deep catering business functions providing an order for dinner quick cashier for fast food aggregating orders for the three big take-out platforms and the purchase of coupons by Meituan Group it can completely cover the business scene of the catering industry.

KDS is a post-cooking management system. The product goal is to improve the efficiency of communication between the front and back kitchens improve the efficiency of production improve the efficiency of food delivery save consumables reduce the cost of errors and reduce labor costs. K-MOBILE is a converged APP that targets mobile catering services and mobile management. It not only includes basic services such as regular opening ordering ordering and collection but also includes products. The management dimension of management inventory management store management etc.; providing efficient mobile services and convenient mobile management for merchants is a value proposition that K-MOBILE product line has always adhered to.
